<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="css/tips.css"></head><body><p><b>View Spring bean documentation</b></p><p>You can access Spring bean documentation directly from the editor. Place the caret at a bean, press <span class="shortcut">&shortcut:SelectIn;</span>, and select <span class="control">Spring Beans</span>. The <span class="control">Spring</span> tool window opens showing you all available information.</p><p class="image"><img src="images/spring_open_bean.png" alt="Viewing Spring bean documentation" style="border: 1px solid #55555;" /></p></body></html>